arguments.body: Hi Dora, I just visited your website (www.dora-website.com). I like the simplicity of your personal site, but I think it could benefit from more content about your background, interests, or projects. The contact information is clear, which is great! Let me know if you'd like more specific feedback.

Hi Eve, I just checked out your blog (www.eve-blog.com). I like that you've shared your passion for hiking! It would be great to see some of your hiking experiences, photos, or recommendations for trails. The simple layout works well, but perhaps adding more content sections would make it more engaging. Let me know if you'd like more detailed suggestions!
